def_en: Overtime is time that you spend doing your job in addition to your normal working hours.
If you say that someone is working overtime to do something, you mean that they are using a lot of energy, effort, or enthusiasm trying to do it.

def_cn: （体育比赛中为决胜负而延长的）加时赛
def_en: Overtime is an additional period of time that is added to the end of a sports match in which the two teams are level, as a way of allowing one of the teams to win.
